source 'https://rubygems.org'

### Environment variable version overrrides

# puppet
puppet_version = ENV.key?('PUPPET_VERSION') ? "= #{ENV['PUPPET_VERSION']}" : \
  '= 4.8.2' # from puppet enterprise 3.2.3


### Gem requirements
gem 'rake'
